content.content:
The policy covers phones that;

+ have a screen size of less than 7 inches (measured diagonally);
+ are the manufacturer’s standard design and specification;
+ cannot be used as a satellite phone; and
+ have not have been manufactured wholly or partly from precious or semi precious metals, stones or crystals.

Please remember your mobile phone insurance covers your phone only – that’s the phone you use on a daily basis. It does not extend to phones used on a daily basis by family members or friends even if you pay the bill.
